                <title>瞎扯 · 如何正确地吐槽</title>
                <link>http://daily.zhihu.com/story/9791330</link>
                <description>瞎扯 · 你和你家宠物发生过什么有趣的事？ Q：你和你家宠物发生过什么有趣的事？ @Luna rossa ：冬天，这位十几岁的姑娘觉得冷了。 Q：你敢把相册里面第 5 张照片发出来吗？ @汤姆迪尔 ：抖音，一个卖蜂蜜的直播间主播。看样子蜂蜜应该是真的。 Q：如何看待现在中小学生嘴里的「那咋了」、「包的」、「受着呗」、「因为我善」等等用语？ @半佛仙人 ：我觉得大家更文明了，一代比一代强。我们小时候…</description>
                <content:encoded><![CDATA[<div class="main-img" style="margin-bottom: 20px;"><img src="https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e38d29d44440ef6f0bb1d6fab68ae2bd.jpg?source=8673f162" style="max-width:100%; border-radius: 8px;"></div><div class="main-wrap content-wrap">
<div class="headline">

<div class="img-place-holder"></div>



</div>

<div class="content-inner">




<div class="question">
<h2 class="question-title">瞎扯 · 你和你家宠物发生过什么有趣的事？</h2>

<div class="answer">

<div class="content">
<p>Q：<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/330608341/answer/2033193466570747982" target="_blank">你和你家宠物发生过什么有趣的事？</a></p>
<blockquote>
<div class="css-1gomreu"><a class="UserLink-link" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/1ce7d8a96291fa6f4061053a59a0bc8b" target="_blank">@Luna rossa</a></div>
 ：冬天，这位十几岁的姑娘觉得冷了。</blockquote>
<figure>
<div class="RichText-ConditionalImagePortal"><img class="content-image" src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-210f6d6e15bee4971ff197766ca13a78_1440w.jpg" alt=""></div>
<figcaption></figcaption></figure>
<p>Q：<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/1918448137854494426/answer/2034208881375721125" target="_blank">你敢把相册里面第 5 张照片发出来吗？</a></p>
<blockquote>
<div class="css-1gomreu"><a class="UserLink-link" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/f101c4b032262a30aec148143349021c" target="_blank">@汤姆迪尔</a></div>
 ：抖音，一个卖蜂蜜的直播间主播。看样子蜂蜜应该是真的。</blockquote>
<figure>
<div class="RichText-ConditionalImagePortal"><img class="content-image" src="https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-632f852cb19e35962f0efb8be891748f_1440w.jpg" alt=""></div>
<figcaption></figcaption></figure>
<p>Q：<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/1975994449046831682/answer/2033287844316320694" target="_blank">如何看待现在中小学生嘴里的</a>「<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/1975994449046831682/answer/2033287844316320694" target="_blank">那咋了</a>」<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/1975994449046831682/answer/2033287844316320694" target="_blank">、</a>「<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/1975994449046831682/answer/2033287844316320694" target="_blank">包的</a>」<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/1975994449046831682/answer/2033287844316320694" target="_blank">、</a>「<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/1975994449046831682/answer/2033287844316320694" target="_blank">受着呗</a>」<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/1975994449046831682/answer/2033287844316320694" target="_blank">、</a>「<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/1975994449046831682/answer/2033287844316320694" target="_blank">因为我善</a>」<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/1975994449046831682/answer/2033287844316320694" target="_blank">等等用语？</a></p>
<blockquote>
<div class="css-1gomreu"><a class="UserLink-link" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/ec7b66af7cd513fd3659d3c3ee347a77" target="_blank">@半佛仙人</a></div>
 ：我觉得大家更文明了，一代比一代强。<br>我们小时候那个顺口溜，童谣和段子放在今天都够封号的。</blockquote>
<p>Q：<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/440965402/answer/1948314860350837171" target="_blank"> 走夜路被一只黄鼠狼拦住问话时，你该如何脱身？</a></p>
<blockquote>
<div class="css-1gomreu"><a class="UserLink-link" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/664aff4c13d84e9f62d21ec10290c67a" target="_blank">@雨中的葡萄</a></div>
 ：抓住了抓住了。浪费了我十多张粘鼠板<br>好消息。已经招了。<br>它承认我是公务员了</blockquote>
<figure>
<div class="RichText-ConditionalImagePortal"><img class="content-image" src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3159250ded254d2022b13e39e6de3e35_1440w.jpg" alt=""></div>
<figcaption></figcaption></figure>
<p>Q：<a class="internal" href="https://www.zhihu.com/question/1919714647054980135/answer/1949481287355184576" target="_blank">妻子收藏了带辐射的花岗岩如何劝她丢弃?</a></p>
<blockquote>
<div class="css-1gomreu"><a class="UserLink-link" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/a4fc6242be5999478e859f1fb8673541" target="_blank">@高松 燈</a></div>
 ：带辐射的花岗岩？猜你找的是这个。</blockquote>
<figure>
<div class="RichText-ConditionalImagePortal"><img class="content-image" src="https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e92b26026f5adf5b8d90139a10f706bb_1440w.jpg" alt=""></div>
<figcaption>巡航速度 1.5 马赫，末端速度 2.5 马赫，携带核战斗部，是花岗岩中的豪杰</figcaption></figure>
<hr>
<p>✨恭喜你发现了（即将成为）知乎最好笑的地方，加入「扯点好笑的」圈子，每天看点段子梗图神回复，一起一本正经地胡说八道吧！</p>
<div class="RichText-LinkCardContainer"><a class="LinkCard new css-2l69ki" href="https://www.zhihu.com/ring/host/1979586347799950567?tab=new&amp;tab_id=0" target="_blank"><span class="LinkCard-contents"><span class="LinkCard-title two-line">扯点好笑的</span><span class="LinkCard-desc LinkCard-desc-wrapper"><br></span></span></a></div>
</div>
</div>


</div>


